## 6. Endpoint Usage

### Manual Flow

### Create product

`POST /api/products`

Use for manual add-product flow.

### Load product details

`GET /api/products/{id}`

Use this as the source of truth for detail and edit screens.

### Update product

`PUT /api/products/{id}`

Use when the app already has the numeric product id.

### Barcode Flow

### Resolve scanned barcode

`GET /api/inventory-manager/barcode/products/{barcode}/resolve`

This is the first call after scan.

Possible behavior:

- barcode matches base product
- barcode matches active variant
- barcode does not exist

