### Create product from barcode flow

`POST /api/inventory-manager/barcode/products`

Use this after scan when `exists = false`.

Request body uses the same product payload contract as manual create.

### Load full product by barcode

`GET /api/inventory-manager/barcode/products/{barcode}`

Use when you already know the base product barcode exists and you want the full product payload again.

### Update product by barcode

`PUT /api/inventory-manager/barcode/products/{barcode}`

Use when the screen started from a known base product barcode and you want barcode-based update.

Important note:

- this endpoint updates by base product barcode
- variant barcode may resolve the parent product for viewing, but mutation by barcode should use the parent product barcode

